++++++-## 2026-06-22 — Software Engineer → Dev Migration
+++++++## 2026-06-28 — Sprint 2.3 — Context Budget Reporting Frozen
++++++ 
++++++ ### Date
++++++-2026-06-22
+++++++2026-06-28
++++++ 
++++++ ### Source
++++++-`#provenance: root/BUILD_LOG.md` (Phase 3 + Decision D003)
